installation(first time):
    1. pip install -r requirements.txt
    2. move config.py.example -> config.py
    3. edit config.py
    4. edit postfix/master.cf
    5. edit postfix/main.cf
    6. reload postfix

add email-messanger binding:
    1. edit config.py
    2. add mail address to /etc/aliases
    3. command `newaliases`
    4. edit postfix/header_checks
    5. reload postfix

